        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Reduce your search space</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Fix your environment</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Set the system up so you always win</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Embrace the suck</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Sometimes do nothing</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Treat study as play and</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Sleep your way to better knowledge</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
